text: José Montilla Aguilera (born 15 January 1955 in Iznájar, Córdoba, Spain) is a Spanish politician who is currently a member of the Spanish Senate.Notícia del nomenament de Montilla com a senador He was the 128th President of Generalitat de Catalunya. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the Government of Catalonia
title: José Montilla
